OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after pictured
OL,4,Cgrinning in front of cannabis farm
OL,6,FA drug dealer who considered himself
OL,7,F"untouchable" has been jailed after he
OL,8,Fwas pictured grinning in front of his
OL,9,Fhuge cannabis farm.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) raided
OL,12,Fthe home of Usman Alam in Rochdale on
OL,13,F5 January 2022, where they discovered
OL,14,Fcannabis, weighing scaled, and three
OL,15,Fmobile phones.
OL,17,FThe phones contained a wealth of
OL,18,Fevidence connecting Alam to the supply
OL,19,Fof cocaine and cannabis over a four-
OL,20,Fyear period.
