OL,6,FGMP officers say the texts also showed
OL,7,FAlam was involved in the production of
OL,8,Fcannabis across England, as well as
OL,9,Fstreet-level drug dealing across
OL,10,FGreater Manchester.
OL,12,FOfficers also examined Alam's bank
OL,13,Faccount and discovered it received
OL,14,F#370,216 without any record of
OL,15,Flegitimate wage transfers.
