OL,6,FManchester Crown Court heard how Alam
OL,7,Falso stabbed and assaulted one of his
OL,8,Fdrug dealers in 2024. Alam accused the
OL,9,Fvictim of stealing drugs from him,
OL,10,Fafter an amount of cannabis was stolen
OL,11,Fa few days prior.
OL,13,FHe then head-butted the victim before
OL,14,Ftaking a knife and striking him with
OL,15,Fthe handle numerous times, slicing and
OL,16,Fcutting him.
OL,18,FLater the same day, Alam made threats
OL,19,Fto "shoot" everyone and "bomb houses"
OL,20,Fof family members associated with the
OL,21,Fvictim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
