OL,6,FAlam pleaded guilty to being concerned
OL,7,Fin the supply of cocaine, being
OL,8,Fconcerned in the supply of cannabis
OL,9,Fand possession of cannabis with intent
OL,10,Fto supply at Manchester Crown Court.
OL,12,FHe also pleaded guilty to Section 20
OL,13,Fassault (grievous bodily harm without
OL,14,Fintent) and making threats to kill
OL,15,Ffollowing the incident last year.
OL,17,FAlam, of Law Street, Rochdale, was
OL,18,Fjailed for six years and three months.
