OL,6,FDetective Inspector Richard Castley,
OL,7,Ffrom GMP's Serious Crime Division,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This sentencing sends a clear
OL,9,Fmessage that drug-related crime will
OL,10,Fnot be tolerated.
OL,12,F"Over a four-year period, this
OL,13,Findividual amassed nearly #400,000
OL,14,Fthrough his illegal drug operations.
OL,16,F"The violence he showed by the brutal
OL,17,Fbeating of someone he merely suspected
OL,18,Fof stealing from him, demonstrates the
OL,19,Fdangerous nature of Alam and how he
OL,20,Fthinks he is untouchable and not to be
OL,21,Fcrossed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
